Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 
1. Aniccavagga 
6. Bāhirānattasutta 
“Rūpā, bhikkhave, anattā. 
Yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. 
Saddā … pe … 
gandhā … 
rasā … 
phoṭṭhabbā … 
dhammā anattā. 
Yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. 
Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … 
nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. 
Chaṭṭhaṃ. 
